Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（用大屁股诱惑的女教师）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（由朝阳老师亲自教授关于性爱合体特别课程)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（第一节课） （在保健室的诱惑战术）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先坐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在看哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用装傻啦   装傻?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直看老师屁股对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看屁股?没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错觉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我发觉到你一直盯着看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要承认吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会平时都盯着我屁股看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常?没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像在上课时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就直盯着我屁股看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实一点比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会期待有这种事情发生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在靠近点看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不老实说的话就到此为止哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢还是讨厌老师的屁股?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个大屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:06:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直很想摸对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随你想怎么摸都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是想摸吗?   对,想摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快点老师可是要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想摸的话就多摸一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你平时就盯着看的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多摸一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人如果摸了像我这种屁股是不是就会很有元气?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有元气是指?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有元气的东西吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元气?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那来玩更有趣的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蹲下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着,靠近一点  很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是老师的屁股什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股的柔软度如何?  多观看一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师用屁股的肉夹住你的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股很爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平时就盯着看对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有现在,屁股可以如你所想那样子摸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如我所想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随你想怎么摸都可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得好清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连老师的屁眼都看得很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在张大一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.79,0:11:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师    什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好去舔老师的屁股吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害,屁眼都湿湿的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:13:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你的口水把这个屁股舔湿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股很大可能会舔得较辛苦要努力去舔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好下流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再舔深一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁眼细缝也要去舔湿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.14,0:14:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好下流的舔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师的屁股好吃吗?  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来不是用嘴巴而是用你下面这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来享受老师的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这根鸡巴一直都硬邦邦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夹住了,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像在乳交一样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒的声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你勃起的鸡巴弄得老师的大屁股好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么处理这根勃起的鸡巴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样挺着勃起的鸡巴回家?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐到老师说好为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.54,0:17:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会忍受不住吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龟头好红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且血管充血状态好明显
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睾丸怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舔的太激烈更受不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍住喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以再爽一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以在爽一点喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样子会射出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样舔很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙,要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,要射了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.94,0:23:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.06,0:24:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射的还真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.19,0:24:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,积了那么久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.11,0:24:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好念书才行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.81,0:24:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.88,0:24:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会念书
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.72,0:24:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看老师屁股可以,不过也要念书
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.43,0:25:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.88,0:25:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(第2节课）（教授性爱课程）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.58,0:26:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?你怎么还在啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.36,0:26:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被惩罚留在学校做事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.50,0:26:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事都做完了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.33,0:26:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点没做完
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.17,0:26:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做的还真慢耶
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.18,0:26:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.05,0:26:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上课时
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.82,0:26:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你光盯着老师屁股看成绩才会这样差对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.50,0:26:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有,才没有那会事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.00,0:26:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我上次不是叫你要好好念书
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.31,0:27:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你老是学不会那我就没办法早点走
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.82,0:27:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.19,0:27:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么负责?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.23,0:27:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.27,0:27:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么负责?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.04,0:27:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,负责?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.30,0:27:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把老师宝贵的时间还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.18,0:27:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.11,0:27:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么具体负起责任呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.52,0:27:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么负责?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.89,0:27:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想摸屁股心神不宁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.76,0:27:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手想伸过来摸屁股对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.83,0:27:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.87,0:27:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那么喜欢屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.77,0:28:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那么喜欢屁股吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.64,0:28:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.71,0:28:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就连上课时手都想伸进去摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.82,0:28:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个大变态耶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.20,0:28:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.96,0:28:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那么喜欢我这屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.07,0:28:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为老师的屁股很美
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.41,0:28:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很介意接下来的事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.85,0:28:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.82,0:28:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好好的说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.52,0:28:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看老师的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.23,0:28:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.86,0:29:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看老师的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.27,0:29:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再大声一点说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.04,0:29:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看老师的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.26,0:29:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你最喜欢的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.90,0:29:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.47,0:29:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠近点看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.42,0:29:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.29,0:29:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师都穿这样来学校吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.86,0:30:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿这样子脱掉是会让人更兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.83,0:30:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.68,0:30:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想摸
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.11,0:30:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.32,0:30:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以摸,只能看喔  怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.39,0:30:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能看
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.27,0:30:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.00,0:31:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.10,0:31:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.92,0:31:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.43,0:31:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边也要
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.97,0:32:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股长得很不错对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.65,0:32:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么硬硬的\N被摩擦的关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.63,0:32:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就勃起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.45,0:33:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.38,0:33:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勃起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.35,0:33:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是诚实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.77,0:33:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.86,0:33:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.70,0:34:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用舌头来回舔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.78,0:34:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗?    对
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.14,0:34:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有另一边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.11,0:34:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.43,0:35:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要爽对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.57,0:35:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想用老师的屁股爽对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.91,0:35:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴勃起成这样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.50,0:35:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我看勃起的鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.18,0:35:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.86,0:36:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害,勃起成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.91,0:36:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脚张开
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.26,0:36:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师用屁股来摩擦鸡巴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.54,0:37:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.55,0:37:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到勃起成这样的鸡巴 真令人兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.24,0:38:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.11,0:38:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.94,0:38:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来摸奶子
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.13,0:39:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经到了极限对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.94,0:39:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.84,0:39:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.18,0:39:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再让你更爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.38,0:39:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果放进这小穴里
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.62,0:39:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想会更爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.59,0:39:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那根勃起的鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.10,0:39:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想插进老师湿润小穴看看嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.17,0:39:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想插
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.71,0:39:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要插吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.65,0:39:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来看老师的小穴有多湿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.42,0:40:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.86,0:40:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在靠近一点看
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.54,0:40:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好湿润
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.60,0:40:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种距离看不清楚吧  太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.81,0:40:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.25,0:40:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好地舔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.17,0:40:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要把老师的小穴舔到湿哒哒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.78,0:40:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.78,0:41:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不够湿哒哒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.79,0:41:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.16,0:41:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面更温暖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.03,0:41:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.77,0:41:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何?里面更温暖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.71,0:41:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好湿润
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.33,0:42:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师的小穴只是用手指无法满足
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.70,0:42:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你那根勃起的鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.61,0:42:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来插老师的小穴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.93,0:42:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插进来
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.13,0:42:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得好清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.60,0:43:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师这里...湿哒哒的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.38,0:43:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想被你那根勃起的鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.72,0:43:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.40,0:43:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插入了  还没有只有龟头而已
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.74,0:43:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光龟头就那么爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.57,0:43:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.14,0:43:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有龟头插入而已
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.88,0:43:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光这无法满足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.53,0:44:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.60,0:44:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着你鸡巴插入的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.30,0:44:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师小穴如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.00,0:44:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.00,0:44:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.46,0:45:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要爽就用力动腰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.70,0:45:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.60,0:45:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用你勃起的鸡巴用力插老师的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.23,0:45:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师可是还没有满足喔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.01,0:45:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让老师看插入的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.59,0:46:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.00,0:46:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.31,0:46:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴再用力插
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.34,0:46:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.25,0:46:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力干出声音来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.39,0:46:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.84,0:47:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正面也来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.29,0:47:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来,让小穴多品尝你的鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.07,0:47:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.40,0:47:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽,鸡巴再插深一点
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.10,0:48:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插深一点
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.51,0:48:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对,再用力插老师的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.55,0:48:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.43,0:49:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊!小穴和奶子都好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.01,0:49:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.30,0:50:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.08,0:50:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.55,0:50:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来压住老师的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.32,0:50:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.79,0:50:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再压住
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.12,0:50:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.40,0:50:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师的脸和小穴都看得很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.44,0:50:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样子鸡巴插进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.11,0:50:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请给我你勃起的鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.70,0:51:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.35,0:51:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何?在平时上课的教室里做会很兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.72,0:51:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.67,0:51:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.07,0:51:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.51,0:52:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴插进了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.04,0:52:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得到这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.64,0:52:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.96,0:52:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.31,0:53:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.09,0:53:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.63,0:53:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来这样子插
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.87,0:53:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.74,0:53:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.51,0:53:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用勃起的鸡巴用力顶到子宫好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.03,0:54:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.76,0:54:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手过来摸
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.17,0:54:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.13,0:55:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.13,0:55:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴插得好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.04,0:55:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴很爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.54,0:55:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.54,0:55:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.08,0:56:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴插得好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.23,0:56:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力揉搓屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.97,0:56:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.41,0:56:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.61,0:57:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉小穴再收缩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.81,0:57:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.46,0:57:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你平时上课时都不专心光盯着老师屁股看对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.44,0:58:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师的大屁股就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.45,0:58:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在多玩弄我的屁股吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.99,0:58:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.17,0:58:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.55,0:58:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.75,0:58:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精液要射出来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.36,0:58:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精液射在老师的屁股上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.16,0:59:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.74,0:59:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.62,0:59:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒,滴下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.24,0:59:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多精液啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.72,0:59:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射好多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.25,0:59:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个无可救药的学生
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.70,1:00:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（第3节课）（肉体观察教学）
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.70,1:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.97,1:06:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这什么声音
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.51,1:08:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.29,1:08:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.13,1:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（第4节课）（教授性耐力）
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.51,1:09:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.71,1:09:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不准你回去
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.35,1:09:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下来  怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.38,1:09:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再保健室里偷窥的人是你对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.69,1:09:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.52,1:10:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.39,1:10:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.63,1:10:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你躲藏得很好嘛?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.96,1:10:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被我看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.93,1:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你偷偷摸摸的看
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.77,1:10:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想说那是什么怪声音
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.44,1:10:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实招了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.21,1:10:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.41,1:10:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你色眯眯偷偷摸摸的看
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.69,1:10:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在保健室里偷偷摸摸的看我
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.23,1:10:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.97,1:10:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勃起了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.81,1:10:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手拿开
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.75,1:11:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在保健室里色眯眯的偷窥
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.02,1:11:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴才硬起来对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.97,1:11:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.47,1:11:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要给你上特别的课程
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.67,1:11:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...老师要做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.81,1:11:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上课啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.32,1:11:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是上课喔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.35,1:11:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师等等
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.69,1:11:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在要教你忍耐力
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.16,1:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐力喔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.54,1:11:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是上课喔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.94,1:12:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.88,1:12:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.95,1:12:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.19,1:12:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.29,1:12:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光看就那么兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.99,1:12:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里有点
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.59,1:12:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龟头好红
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.00,1:13:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.18,1:13:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子弄
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.48,1:13:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子弄不行吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.39,1:13:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师等等
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.17,1:13:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在教你忍耐力喔
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.44,1:13:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐喔
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.28,1:13:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会有吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.62,1:13:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师等等
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.87,1:14:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根部很敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.25,1:14:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不行,再继续
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.65,1:14:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.92,1:14:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.56,1:14:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐着
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.28,1:14:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对这个很有兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.76,1:15:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摩擦噢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.07,1:15:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬鸡巴正摩擦着老师的奶头喔
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.95,1:15:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬鸡巴正搓弄着老师的奶子
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.01,1:16:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师太激烈了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.95,1:16:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄过头了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.92,1:16:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,会出来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.02,1:16:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出来
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.93,1:16:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样子?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.60,1:16:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.97,1:16:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在教你忍耐力啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.67,1:16:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再教你忍耐
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.08,1:16:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.52,1:16:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以射喔
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.06,1:16:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.60,1:16:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.55,1:17:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴一直跳动想要射啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.09,1:17:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.26,1:17:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.10,1:17:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等上完课你想要射就自己滋味吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.75,1:17:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,要射了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.15,1:17:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龟头好红啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.42,1:17:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看鸡巴硬成这样子
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.83,1:18:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勃起的好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.14,1:18:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会是受虐狂吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.85,1:18:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.30,1:18:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.01,1:18:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.21,1:18:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么  你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.25,1:18:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以射吗
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.32,1:18:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.19,1:18:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.99,1:19:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.01,1:19:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.61,1:19:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这根鸡巴这么有元气啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.85,1:19:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.79,1:19:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还这么有元气啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.76,1:20:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.66,1:20:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能射
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.60,1:20:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差一点就射了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.52,1:20:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,可以射吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.46,1:20:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.99,1:20:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上忍耐力的课
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.07,1:20:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,要设立啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.42,1:21:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样子还不行
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.93,1:21:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧  对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.60,1:21:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改天再上课
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.14,1:21:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样结束吗
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.84,1:21:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的课到此为止
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.48,1:21:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师等等啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.40,1:22:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.50,1:22:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我东西忘了拿
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.64,1:22:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了什么东西呢
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.01,1:22:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了拿体育服
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.14,1:22:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,体育服?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.15,1:22:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看！有吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.52,1:22:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我有放在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.92,1:22:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.16,1:22:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.97,1:22:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.24,1:23:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.82,1:23:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.89,1:23:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷看人换衣服兴奋成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.26,1:23:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.10,1:23:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起有点兴奋
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.64,1:23:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.97,1:23:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋勃起了想怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.98,1:23:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才一直想要射对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.88,1:23:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上忍耐力课程的时候    对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.72,1:23:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那么喜欢屁股啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.53,1:23:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很喜欢屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.70,1:24:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.51,1:24:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这个啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.68,1:24:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那么喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.68,1:24:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个也喜欢?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.52,1:24:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再大力一点
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.00,1:24:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个变态耶
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.37,1:24:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勃起啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.64,1:24:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.88,1:24:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这根鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.35,1:24:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会硬到什么程度呢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.24,1:25:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你不是很想要
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.61,1:25:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要这样吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.52,1:25:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你想要这个吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.10,1:25:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不管你要不要
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.55,1:26:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难受吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.35,1:26:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难受对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.89,1:26:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股弄得很难受啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.39,1:26:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.34,1:26:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难受吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.27,1:26:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再让你更难受吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.77,1:26:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.55,1:27:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我可是再说教耶
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.19,1:27:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你下流的鸡巴变成这样?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.43,1:27:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么鸡巴变成这样?   对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.15,1:27:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力一点
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.05,1:27:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.52,1:27:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?怎么了啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.79,1:27:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太强了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.26,1:28:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.90,1:28:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一副很爽的表情
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.31,1:28:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.18,1:28:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?突然这么安静
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.62,1:28:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.49,1:28:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然变这么安静
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.68,1:29:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.88,1:29:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.92,1:29:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样搓奶头有很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.96,1:29:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.74,1:29:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.84,1:29:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢搓弄奶头啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.98,1:29:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.92,1:29:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那这一边呢
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.52,1:30:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真碍事
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.39,1:30:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.13,1:30:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你刚才不是一直想射吗
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.77,1:30:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些都还只是前戏喔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.76,1:30:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.51,1:30:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这根鸡巴比刚才更勃起耶
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.08,1:31:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才上忍耐力课程的时候想射吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.14,1:31:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不知羞耻的鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.00,1:31:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱摸好吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.37,1:32:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要乱摸好吗?    对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.72,1:32:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.73,1:32:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.30,1:32:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能让你射呢
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.01,1:33:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子弄如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.03,1:33:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里很爽对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.81,1:34:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶头被舔会很兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.28,1:34:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.78,1:34:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶头那么有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.20,1:34:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.76,1:35:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你乱摸的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.96,1:35:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.75,1:35:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴怎么硬成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.23,1:35:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说我的鸡巴是大变态看看
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.26,1:35:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说我的鸡巴是大变态
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.97,1:35:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要那样子说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.87,1:35:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是说过了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.71,1:35:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了那么多羞耻的话
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.81,1:35:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说看看
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.82,1:36:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎样?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.65,1:36:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.95,1:36:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.66,1:36:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.83,1:36:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变态
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.84,1:36:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.94,1:36:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的鸡巴是大变态
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.71,1:36:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听不到     我的鸡巴是大变态
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.22,1:36:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.15,1:36:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.15,1:36:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的鸡巴是大变态
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.60,1:36:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得不错
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.70,1:36:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的赞美
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.64,1:37:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有赞美你吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.11,1:37:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吃我的脚
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.42,1:37:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.20,1:37:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个鸡巴是怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.51,1:37:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你奖励吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.91,1:37:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你最喜欢的大屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.41,1:37:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.55,1:37:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你最喜欢的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.18,1:38:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是最喜欢屁股吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.86,1:38:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要再多舔一点
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.37,1:38:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舌头再上下用力去舔
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.17,1:38:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好舔
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.39,1:39:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要了吗?   想要
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.50,1:39:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.37,1:39:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.21,1:39:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.24,1:39:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱摸奶子
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.96,1:39:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你奖励
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.65,1:40:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴被屁股摩擦如何呢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.82,1:40:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.60,1:40:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.54,1:40:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累了吗?  怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.57,1:40:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.14,1:40:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.08,1:40:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师给我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.42,1:40:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.42,1:40:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.72,1:40:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说不要吗?   对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.23,1:40:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.23,1:40:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子你很有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.74,1:40:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴被老师的屁股这么摩擦
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.68,1:41:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶头这样被搓弄
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.38,1:41:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师等等   什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.22,1:41:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.97,1:41:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.81,1:41:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.49,1:41:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流液体出来了啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.97,1:41:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的话就光大手枪就够了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.71,1:42:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.74,1:42:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光大手枪就够了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.41,1:42:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这根变态的鸡巴
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.48,1:42:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会想要插你的鸡巴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.39,1:42:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,我要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.95,1:42:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能射
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.78,1:42:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.66,1:42:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还可以再忍耐吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.22,1:42:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再上来一点
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.53,1:42:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.53,1:43:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要看你能忍耐到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.11,1:43:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.78,1:43:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对,那个
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.05,1:43:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.40,1:44:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湿淋淋的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.90,1:44:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.34,1:44:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.05,1:44:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.35,1:44:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.49,1:44:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.69,1:44:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.93,1:44:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.33,1:44:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.87,1:44:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可饶不了你喔  对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.54,1:44:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.84,1:44:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插入老师的小穴啊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.55,1:44:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.42,1:45:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.13,1:45:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想说一直硬邦邦的鸡巴插进来是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.68,1:45:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.65,1:45:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变态的鸡巴插入小穴也都一直好硬
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.40,1:45:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.63,1:45:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到插入的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.50,1:45:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会更兴奋对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.27,1:45:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很变态对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.14,1:45:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师太棒了   看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.33,1:46:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.66,1:46:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?小穴很爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.78,1:46:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的小穴有那么爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.79,1:46:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.83,1:46:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多让我看你那很爽的脸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.13,1:46:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很爱看你那表情
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.29,1:47:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.96,1:47:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸡巴再顶了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.37,1:47:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.61,1:47:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换你鸡巴用力往上顶
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.95,1:47:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道怎么动吧    我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.12,1:47:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.33,1:47:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.43,1:47:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.31,1:48:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没完喔
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.42,1:48:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.51,1:49:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:14.74,1:49:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.14,1:49:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想插了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:36.53,1:49:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来看老师的大屁股吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.44,1:49:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.07,1:50:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.84,1:50:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.31,1:50:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师正在爽耶
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.08,1:50:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.78,1:50:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.35,1:50:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.83,1:50:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,好爽,可以在拍打我吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.80,1:50:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要我拍打啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.97,1:50:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就好好拍打你吧
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.31,1:50:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了没用的你
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.75,1:51:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.03,1:51:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再打
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.06,1:51:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再打喔
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.23,1:51:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样没有问题
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.38,1:51:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师只对你的鸡巴兴奋喔
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.64,1:51:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.26,1:52:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.04,1:52:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.67,1:53:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来这里
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.04,1:53:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着换你来
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.95,1:53:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从后面来插
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.32,1:53:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会吗?  没问题
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.86,1:53:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只会鸡巴硬邦邦的
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.46,1:54:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样能满足我吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.66,1:54:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力点
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.23,1:54:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前都这样做爱吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.54,1:54:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.59,1:54:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.49,1:54:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腰再用力动
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.40,1:54:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师的背部好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.97,1:54:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你插入老师小穴里的鸡巴也很棒
Dialogue: 0,1:55:02.46,1:55:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.46,1:55:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小穴里面好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:28.28,1:55:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插好深,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:55:38.73,1:55:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再用力,再激烈一点插
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.43,1:55:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.21,1:55:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以喔！要打几次都可以
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.38,1:56:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要来打了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.66,1:56:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这变态
Dialogue: 0,1:56:19.83,1:56:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.00,1:56:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以再加油吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.27,1:56:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.98,1:56:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加油啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.44,1:57:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.54,1:57:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:07.95,1:57:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就射吧
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.89,1:57:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过要射在屁股上
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.79,1:57:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射在老师的大屁股上吧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.54,1:58:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.94,1:58:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.18,1:58:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:58:46.95,1:58:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把老师的屁股弄成这样
Dialogue: 0,1:58:51.72,1:58:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄脏了喔
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.15,1:58:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.99,1:59:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会原谅你吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.27,1:59:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.03,1:59:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会原谅你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.39,1:59:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛,但太爽了

